{"tid":1250957,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"一人一信投訴tvb不實報道","createTime":"2019-06-22T09:52:50.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-25T03:03:36.000Z","uid":223868,"like":61,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"119744be78035966993ff3db6ee023a8fd25a657","tid":1250957,"uid":223868,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T09:52:50.000Z","msg":"請麻煩大家一人一信投訴tvb不實報道6月21日包圍警察總部運動，導致報道嚴重偏袒警方和政府，非公平公正傳媒所為，投訴信範本如下：<br />\n<br />\n無線電視台tvb於6月21至22日的新聞報導時間在全港報導，指示威者集會阻礙救援警總內的人，然而現場多人透露事實是警方拒開閘，阻礙救援組，拖至午夜直至前線示威者和警方斡旋20分鐘，警方才肯開閘讓救援組內進。（實情已在有線電視現場直播中完全客觀報導）。因為無綫新聞報導不全面，扭曲真相，散播不客觀事實導致觀眾無法接收客觀事實，示威者的行動被抹黑。<br />\n<br />\n強烈譴責無綫新聞報導不全面，散播不客觀事實，愚弄大眾。<br />\n請有關當局處理，捍衛新聞自由。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n投訴表格：<a href=\"https://apps.coms-auth.hk/apps/broadcasting_complaint/index.aspx?lang=2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fapps.coms-auth.hk%2Fapps%2Fbroadcasting_complaint%2Findex.aspx%3Flang%3D2&d=Hh5C2Wm8JWR9usSbwEl%2Bhz8W653rZVWOX%2F4zqp%2BjK3Y%3D&h=8d2b770a\" target=\"_blank\">https://apps.coms-auth.hk/apps/broadcasting_complaint/index.aspx?lang=2</a>"},{"pid":"da3b1ab1d1682261b0fa99e54bb30c9ac870602c","tid":1250957,"uid":223868,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T09:59:49.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"759931f49ef7e2617274b6a37d1a4807cb95f227","tid":1250957,"uid":61830,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T10:03:53.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"6cf9ab8132a05e3082e45543f52d1e08b66099ac","tid":1250957,"uid":28870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T10:07:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"77e3ff0c872dff2c194506ef214ee6e3155be5a5","tid":1250957,"uid":22628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T10:08:08.000Z","msg":"已投 推"},{"pid":"cd27f18308049750e913f193f51cb52a5b06371e","tid":1250957,"uid":95181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T10:10:30.000Z","msg":"<